(20, 'Vocab list 1', 'JeweledVessel39', '{\"desc\":\"Week 1-2 vocab\",\"contnt\":{\"to regard with extreme repugnance: to loathe; to turn aside or keep away from esp. In scorn or shuddering fear: reject.\":{\"type\":\"txt\",\"ans\":[\"Abhor\"]},\"the bottomless gulf, pit, or chaos of the old cosmologies; an immeasurably deep gulf or great space\":{\"type\":\"txt\",\"ans\":[\"Abyss\"]},\"to go with or attend; to perform an accompaniment to or for\":{\"type\":\"txt\",\"ans\":[\"accompany\"]},\"to come into existence as a legally enforceable claim; to collect or accumulate\":{\"type\":\"txt\",\"ans\":[\"accrue\"]},\"a saying often in metaphorical form that embodies a common observation\":{\"type\":\"txt\",\"ans\":[\"adage\"]},\"unshakable or unmovable, especially in opposition\":{\"type\":\"txt\",\"ans\":[\"adamant\"]},\"to give support or maintain loyalty; to be consistent; to hold fast or stick by or as if by gluing\":{\"type\":\"txt\",\"ans\":[\"adhere\"]},\"to indicate duties or obligations to; to express warning or disapproval to in an earnest, gentle manner\":{\"type\":\"txt\",\"ans\":[\"admonish\"]},\"the cause of persistent pain or distress; great suffering\":{\"type\":\"txt\",\"ans\":[\"affliction\"]},\"nimbleness, dexterity\":{\"type\":\"txt\",\"ans\":[\"agility\"]},\"a leisurely walk\":{\"type\":\"txt\",\"ans\":[\"amble\"]},\"generally agreeable: having a friendly disposition\":{\"type\":\"txt\",\"ans\":[\"amiable\"]},\"showing a likeness that allows one to draw an analogy: comparable\":{\"type\":\"txt\",\"ans\":[\"analogous\"]},\"absence of government; absence of order\":{\"type\":\"txt\",\"ans\":[\"anarchy\"]},\"to attach as a quality,  consequence\":{\"type\":\"txt\",\"ans\":[\"annex\"]},\"to cause to be of no effect; to regard as of no consequence; to cause to cease to exist; to destroy a considerable part of\":{\"type\":\"txt\",\"ans\":[\"annihilate\"]},\"to apply oil to as a sacred rite esp. For consecration; to consecrate\":{\"type\":\"txt\",\"ans\":[